---
title: Smokey Crumbed Chicken & Apple Cos Salad with Parmesan Cheese & Herby-Mayo Dressing
description: Get ready for a deliciously crunchy twist on your weeknight dinner! This crumbed chicken is perfectly golden, crispy, and oh-so-juicy. Paired with a fresh, crisp apple salad, this dish has the perfect balance of textures and flavours.

